00:29:51.200 --> 00:29:52.330
Kapag tumigil ang ulan,

00:29:52.550 --> 00:29:54.080
hahanapin natin ulit si Bai Ze.

00:29:54.110 --> 00:29:54.970
anong sabi mo

00:29:57.830 --> 00:29:58.360
Sige.

