00:30:32.070 --> 00:30:33.070
o Daoist shrine.

00:30:33.480 --> 00:30:35.010
Sa paghusga sa hitsura nito,

00:30:35.200 --> 00:30:37.320
hindi ito mukhang walang laman.

00:30:38.480 --> 00:30:39.340
Hindi ito walang laman.

